#
# -----------------------------------------------------
#					DEPENDENCIES
# -----------------------------------------------------

mrVision module needs the following modules

- python			(version 2.7)
- pyxb 				(http://sourceforge.net/projects/pyxb/)
- python-qt4
- python-opencv


# -----------------------------------------------------
#					INSTALLATION
# -----------------------------------------------------

WINDOWS:
1.	Download python and every package from the corresponding
	website and install it.

LINUX:
1. 	Use apt-get to install python and modules
		sudo apt-get install python python-qt4 python-opencv

2.	Download pyxb from sourceforge, unpack it, open terminal
	in pyxb folder and install it using
		sudo python setup.py install
		
# -----------------------------------------------------
#					USAGE
# -----------------------------------------------------

Start mrVision.py inside src/mrVision using follgowing
command from root directory

	python src/mrVision/mrVision.py